{"tid":673404,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"西遊記兩部曲可唔可以算係最經典既周星馳電影？","createTime":"2018-05-21T20:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T12:41:35.000Z","uid":106799,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"025038d1c3d134f19bb8a64f051af47380721cb3","tid":673404,"uid":106799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T20:36:54.000Z","msg":"月光寶盒同仙履奇緣<br />\n兩集內容環環相扣 慢慢舖陳出一段受命運作弄既愛情 有悲有喜 有笑有淚<br />\n仲有一首點題既主題曲 - 一生所愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Yp_Ir7-hGT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYp_Ir7-hGT8&d=Cf9YCzyxC9ID9a6tD1u72V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=25b012e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Yp_Ir7-hGT8</a><br />\n<br />\nJuno有首金剛圈又好似係講緊依個故事 每次聽到都諗起至尊寶帶金剛圈既獨白 同埋痛到捉唔到紫霞 望住佢飛走果種崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qRP4hZDu09w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqRP4hZDu09w&d=Cf9YCzyxC9ID9a6tD1u72V0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1b992606\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qRP4hZDu09w</a>"},{"pid":"b93b3c2b61deef4d07b1aa1e7d2509a4e399534d","tid":673404,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T20:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7e2afdc75e038adaae0dd5cc6b5b032952d6d1","tid":673404,"uid":106799,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T20:51:33.000Z","msg":"仲有紫霞真係世界級靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/22/045126_0003931302b9f6e25d8c6191ff1c4eb7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F22%2F045126_0003931302b9f6e25d8c6191ff1c4eb7.gif&h=0e79a76f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ca11a9f5185fa2c3ae3c9fa26ae29e0